TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.STAGESALESTRANSACTIONSEQ as STAGESALESTRANSACTIONSEQ, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.GENERICATTRIBUTE32 as GENERICATTRIBUTE32, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.ORDERID as ORDERID, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.EVENTTYPEID as EVENTTYPEID, CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.PRODUCTDESCRIPTION as PRODUCTDESCRIPTION FROM CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION, IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.eventtypeid like 'PA%' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND TO_CHAR(CS_STAGESALESTRANSACTION.COMPENSATIONDATE,'YYYYMM') = TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE ,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYYMM')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: GENERICATTRIBUTE32 = LKP_GENERICATTRIBUTE32 AND ORDERID = LKP_ORDERID AND EVENTTYPEID = LKP_EVENTTYPEID AND PRODUCTDESCRIPTION = LKP_PRODUCTDESCRIPTION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_BUSINESSUNIT.NAME as BU_NAME, CS_POSITION.NAME as POS_NAME FROM CS_POSITION, CS_RULEELEMENTOWNER, cs_businessunit WHERE 1 = 1 and CS_POSITION.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ = CS_RULEELEMENTOWNER.Ruleelementownerseq and CS_RULEELEMENTOWNER.Islast = 1 and CS_RULEELEMENTOWNER.Removedate= to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and CS_POSITION.Removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and CS_POSITION.Islast = 1 and cs_businessunit.mask = CS_RULEELEMENTOWNER.Businessunitmap AND CS_POSITION.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ = cs_businessunit.Processingunitseq
